WEBVTT

00:07.007 --> 00:08.425
A NETFLIX ORIGINAL SERIES

00:12.804 --> 00:14.764
[narrator] <i>It begins like this.</i>

00:16.307 --> 00:19.144
<i>Two billion years ago, an amoeba.</i>

00:20.020 --> 00:22.689
<i>Wait, let's... let's back up.</i>
<i>I've skipped too many connections.</i>

00:23.857 --> 00:27.652
<i>Out of nothing,</i>
<i>in an instant... everything.</i>

00:28.194 --> 00:32.365
<i>An infinite cosmic orgy</i>
<i>of matter and energy,</i>

00:32.449 --> 00:35.285
<i>rubbing, bumping, and grinding together.</i>

00:35.744 --> 00:38.747
<i>There would be no galaxies,</i>
<i>no suns, no planets,</i>

00:39.164 --> 00:42.333
<i>no life without collisions</i>
<i>of heavenly bodies.</i>

00:42.876 --> 00:43.960
<i>Back to our amoeba.</i>

00:45.420 --> 00:49.174
<i>It engulfs a bacterium with unique powers,</i>
<i>and... voil√†.</i>

00:49.758 --> 00:52.927
<i>Earth's first</i>
<i>photosynthesis-enabled organism.</i>

00:53.970 --> 00:55.180
<i>Maybe it was chance.</i>

00:55.889 --> 00:57.307
<i>Maybe it was inevitable.</i>

00:57.932 --> 00:59.642
<i>This one changed amoeba</i>

00:59.726 --> 01:03.104
<i>becomes the ancestor</i>
<i>of every living plant on Earth,</i>

01:03.188 --> 01:05.774
<i>which in turn floods the planet</i>
<i>with oxygen...</i> <i>paving the way</i>
<i>for every other form of life we know...</i>

01:11.613 --> 01:13.490
<i>leading to more souls, more connections,</i>

01:13.573 --> 01:16.910
<i>and therefore more new worlds</i>
<i>branching outward from the first.</i>

01:17.786 --> 01:20.580
<i>These forces of nature,</i>
<i>when they converge,</i>

01:20.663 --> 01:24.501
<i>be they astronomical collisions,</i>
<i>biological unions,</i>

01:24.584 --> 01:28.338
<i>demonstrate the infinite potential</i>
<i>of our connections.</i>

01:29.756 --> 01:33.218
<i>This truth also extends</i>
<i>to the human heart.</i>

01:35.220 --> 01:36.096
Pack of Stuttons.

01:38.723 --> 01:39.682
[clears throat]

01:40.850 --> 01:42.811
No offense,
but how are you gonna pay for these?

01:43.478 --> 01:46.064
I'm gonna use an adBuddy
to cover this purchase.

01:46.940 --> 01:49.776
Those assholes
record client conversations.

01:49.859 --> 01:50.944
AD BUDDY NOT ACCEPTED

01:51.027 --> 01:52.612
National Database of Desires.

01:53.029 --> 01:54.322
The businessmen, ever hear of it?

01:54.405 --> 01:55.990
They know you better than you know you.

01:56.574 --> 01:58.409
-Okay.
-It's not a conspiracy,

01:58.493 --> 01:59.953
just a conspiracy theory.

02:00.036 --> 02:01.246
[narrator] <i>Hypothesis...</i>

02:01.996 --> 02:04.207
<i>all souls are on a quest to connect.</i>

02:06.334 --> 02:07.168
<i>Corollary...</i>

02:07.252 --> 02:09.712
<i>our minds have no awareness of this quest.</i>

02:14.134 --> 02:15.135
Oh.

02:18.179 --> 02:19.013
[sighs]

02:19.764 --> 02:23.101
Did you know that most quarters have been
swallowed and defecated by a human?

02:24.227 --> 02:28.231
[narrator] <i>Hypothesis...</i>
<i>all the worlds that almost were</i>

02:28.314 --> 02:30.608
<i>matter just as much as the world we're in.</i>

02:33.444 --> 02:34.320
<i>Corollary...</i>

02:34.863 --> 02:38.116
<i>these hidden worlds cause us great pain.</i>

02:38.199 --> 02:39.534
...no wallet, no shoes.

02:39.617 --> 02:42.954
No idea how I even really got to Poland
in the first place.

02:43.621 --> 02:45.540
Bro, I'm telling you,

02:45.623 --> 02:48.918
this was seriously such a crazy situation.

02:50.503 --> 02:52.589
Th... From Poland... I was in...

02:52.672 --> 02:55.049
I had no idea...
I had no idea how I got there.

02:55.592 --> 02:57.719
[narrator] <i>Camaraderie, communion,</i>

02:58.595 --> 03:00.597
<i>family, friendship, love, what have you.</i>

03:02.807 --> 03:04.017
[chuckles and sighs]

03:04.100 --> 03:06.019
<i>We're lost without connection.</i>

03:06.102 --> 03:08.146
EVERYTHING TASTES BETTER
WHEN YOU'RE TOGETHER

03:08.271 --> 03:10.148
[woman] <i>...relationships are tough.</i>

03:10.815 --> 03:12.483
<i>Thank you, Friend Proxy.</i>

03:12.567 --> 03:16.154
[narrator]<i> It's quite terrible...</i>
<i>to be alone.</i>

03:17.447 --> 03:19.157
NOT ALL HUGS ARE CREATED EQUAL

03:20.950 --> 03:23.536
<i>Put simply, my goal is to eradicate all...</i>

03:24.662 --> 03:27.582
<i>unnecessary and inefficient forms</i>
<i>of human pain.</i>

03:28.958 --> 03:29.792
<i>Forever.</i>

03:31.252 --> 03:33.254
<i>We must evolve past our suffering.</i>

03:34.714 --> 03:36.841
It's trash, not a handout. Let's move it.

03:38.343 --> 03:39.385
What are you, a cop?

03:40.220 --> 03:42.680
Not much of a difference authority-wise.
Let's go.

03:46.142 --> 03:48.853
MILGRIM INDUSTRIES

03:48.937 --> 03:51.356
[narrator]
<i>My research into this matter is...</i>

03:52.148 --> 03:53.358
<i>of course, ongoing.</i>

