-[man] Are you married?

04:20.093 --> 04:21.344
-No.
-[man] Children?

04:24.681 --> 04:25.765
No.

04:25.848 --> 04:29.018
[man] And can you tell us
about the psychotic break

04:29.102 --> 04:31.396
