08:33.679 --> 08:37.308
<i>Would you like to use an adBuddy</i>
<i>to add funds?</i>

08:37.391 --> 08:38.684
<i>Yes or no?</i>

08:41.938 --> 08:44.232
TIRED OF HERE?
ONE WAY FLIGHTS STARTING AT $1799

08:44.315 --> 08:45.358
<i>Welcome.</i>

08:46.359 --> 08:49.320
AD BUDDY

08:49.403 --> 08:52.990
[man over PA] <i>...train now arriving...</i>

08:53.074 --> 08:55.660
<i>Please step away from the platform edge.</i>

09:01.582 --> 09:04.544
[Ad Buddy] <i>Okay, Mr. Milgrim,</i>
<i>I'm gonna need your attention.</i>

09:05.211 --> 09:06.671
"When tragedy strikes others,

09:06.754 --> 09:09.298
it's sometimes hard to know
what to do until now..."

09:10.258 --> 09:11.092
Owen.

