of a heartbroken family in your region."

09:18.808 --> 09:19.642
YOU ARE HERE

09:20.142 --> 09:22.061
Okay, well, up next,

09:22.144 --> 09:26.023
we got something called
Neberdine Pharmaceuticals.

09:26.107 --> 09:26.941
[clears throat]

09:27.692 --> 09:29.068
"Good afternoon, Owen.

09:29.151 --> 09:32.947
Did you know that your rent comprises
87.2 percent of your annual income?"

09:34.615 --> 09:35.741
Is that actually true?

09:37.618 --> 09:40.997
-I just moved into my own place.
-[Ad Buddy] Manhattan these days...

09:41.497 --> 09:43.624
I'm over in an underground warehouse unit.

09:44.417 --> 09:45.334
Hoboken.

09:46.085 --> 09:48.713
-I actually live in Roosevelt Island.
-Okay, well...

09:49.547 --> 09:51.674
Uh, let's see. Oh-ho-ho.

09:51.757 --> 09:54.677
"A catastrophic interruption
in your professional life,

09:55.136 --> 09:57.054
like a furlough, could ruin you.

09:57.513 --> 10:01.183
Ever thought about supplementing
your income with pharmaceutical testing?"

10:01.517 --> 10:03.561
Friend Proxy.

10:03.644 --> 10:06.147
"Tired of spending your time and energy
making friends?"

10:06.230 --> 10:09.859
[operator] <i>And that is why Daddy's Home</i>
<i>is happy to welcome you, Mr. Milgrim.</i>

10:09.942 --> 10:12.194
[Owen] And I'd have to cover
relocation costs?

10:12.278 --> 10:14.614
[operator] <i>And inherit any potential debt</i>
<i>of the deceased.</i>

10:14.697 --> 10:15.948
That doesn't make sense.

10:16.282 --> 10:17.700
<i>So, that's a yes?</i>

10:18.534 --> 10:19.452
To what?

10:19.535 --> 10:21.037
[operator] <i>It makes perfect sense.</i>

10:21.120 --> 10:23.623
<i>-We are offering you heroism.</i>
-[man] So this is your office area.

10:23.706 --> 10:25.416
Again, it's a question of commitment.

10:25.499 --> 10:27.168
[Owen] Your ad is misleading,

10:27.251 --> 10:30.755
'cause you refer to it
as a volunteer opportunity,

10:30.838 --> 10:32.882
but in the end I'd have to pay.

10:33.341 --> 10:35.217
[operator] <i>But think about</i>
<i>what you'd be getting.</i>

10:35.301 --> 10:37.386
<i>-A wife, lonely, in need.</i>
-[Owen] Yeah.

10:37.470 --> 10:39.680
-[operator] <i>Owen. It's a done deal.</i>
-I have to go.

10:40.181 --> 10:42.892
Rozo did the anonymous
hammerhead from the top down

10:42.975 --> 10:45.895
and came back
with a 12-bullet short-termer.

10:46.312 --> 10:48.648
-When?
-Well, they randomized the pattern.

10:48.731 --> 10:51.359
We've sent out 30 memos on it
since this morning.

10:51.442 --> 10:54.445
Um, so this furlough,
how long does it last?

10:54.945 --> 10:56.697
-It's temporary.
-Right.

10:56.781 --> 10:59.158
So... when am I back?

10:59.533 --> 11:02.745
Oh, I don't know. I was kidding.
It's probably permanent.

11:07.333 --> 11:10.044
I was using your kind of humor,

11:10.127 --> 11:13.589
when you say something you don't mean
and nobody laughs.

11:15.257 --> 11:17.468
It's... Yeah, it's okay. I'll just...

11:18.636 --> 11:20.513
I'll just dip into my savings.

11:25.184 --> 11:26.018
Bye.

11:26.727 --> 11:28.145
[exhales]

11:28.229 --> 11:29.146
[rumbling]

11:34.443 --> 11:36.070
[retching]

11:36.862 --> 11:39.073
[coughing]

11:39.865 --> 11:40.700
[spits]

11:43.953 --> 11:44.870
[coughing]

11:50.960 --> 11:56.632
THE PATTERN IS THE PATTERN

11:59.051 --> 12:00.010
[man] <i>Okay, Owen.</i>

12:00.094 --> 12:02.888
<i>-Do you know what I want to do?</i>
<i>-</i>[Owen] <i>Yes.</i>

12:02.972 --> 12:05.224
[man] <i>Are you sure you know</i>
<i>what I want to do?</i>

12:05.850 --> 12:06.684
[Owen] <i>Yes.</i>

12:06.767 --> 12:10.187
[man] <i>The way this deprogramming works,</i>
<i>it's not an overnight fix.</i>

12:10.271 --> 12:12.398
<i>You have to listen to it like a mantra.</i>

12:12.732 --> 12:16.527
<i>If you start feeling paranoid,</i>
<i>you play this tape right away, okay?</i>

12:17.194 --> 12:18.028
[Owen] <i>Okay.</i>

12:18.446 --> 12:21.240
[man] <i>Now, stop me when I say something</i>
<i>that's not true.</i>

12:21.907 --> 12:23.492
<i>The world sends you messages.</i>

12:24.368 --> 12:25.244
[Owen] <i>Yes.</i>

12:25.327 --> 12:27.204
[man] <i>Words are often code words,</i>

12:27.288 --> 12:30.166
<i>or pass phrases for important secrets.</i>

12:30.666 --> 12:31.500
[Owen] <i>Yes.</i>

12:31.584 --> 12:34.628
[man] <i>You're visited by a brother</i>
<i>no one else in your family is aware of.</i>

12:34.712 --> 12:36.839
<i>A facsimile of your brother Jed.</i>

12:37.381 --> 12:39.133
-[Owen] <i>Yes.</i>
-[man] <i>He sends you messages.</i>

12:39.216 --> 12:42.595
<i>Instructions for important missions</i>
<i>you must accomplish.</i>

12:43.137 --> 12:44.930
[Owen] <i>To see the deeper truth.</i>

12:45.014 --> 12:47.349
[man] <i>He tells you you're meant</i>
<i>to do something big,</i>

12:47.433 --> 12:49.769
<i>something that matters to the world,</i> <i>and that you're not meant to do it alone.</i>

12:52.271 --> 12:54.064
<i>All you need is a partner.</i>

12:55.191 --> 12:56.108
[Owen] <i>Yes.</i>

12:56.192 --> 12:59.069
[woman] <i>You made a promise to me,</i>
<i>and you made a promise to yourself.</i>

12:59.153 --> 13:02.323
<i>You promised we'd golf together</i>
<i>in Hilton Head.</i>

13:02.406 --> 13:05.826
[man] <i>You sense danger all around you,</i>
<i>but you stay disciplined.</i>

13:06.494 --> 13:07.495
<i>A fight's coming.</i>

13:07.578 --> 13:09.955
<i>Something even bigger than this world.</i>

13:10.039 --> 13:12.374
<i>Possibly extending to multiple galaxies.</i>

13:12.458 --> 13:14.710
-[elevator] <i>Fourth floor. Thank you.</i>
-[Owen] <i>Yes.</i>

13:14.794 --> 13:16.253
Hello, Mrs. Finkelstein.

13:16.337 --> 13:17.963
Fuck off, Donovan.

13:18.964 --> 13:20.424
It's, uh... Owen.

13:21.509 --> 13:24.178
-Owen Milgrim...
-Fuck off, Donovan.

13:24.261 --> 13:25.095
Never mind. [man] <i>Good.</i>

13:27.389 --> 13:29.391
<i>Does it feel good to be heard?</i>

13:29.475 --> 13:30.351
[Owen] <i>Yes.</i>

13:30.434 --> 13:34.021
[man] <i>Does it feel good to know that</i>
<i>you're not alone with this information?</i>

13:34.104 --> 13:35.231
[Owen] <i>Yeah.</i>

13:35.314 --> 13:37.191
[man] <i>Will you complete your mission?</i>

13:38.108 --> 13:39.068
[Owen] <i>Maybe.</i>

13:39.401 --> 13:40.861
[man] <i>Am I a trusted messenger?</i>

13:42.404 --> 13:43.239
[Owen] <i>Yes.</i>

13:43.322 --> 13:45.741
[man] <i>Good.</i>
<i>Then here are your real instructions.</i>

13:46.116 --> 13:47.159
<i>Repeat after me.</i> <i>There is no pattern.</i>

13:49.620 --> 13:50.996
[Owen] <i>There is no pattern.</i>

13:51.288 --> 13:53.958
[man] <i>I am vulnerable,</i>
<i>but I am not stupid.</i>

13:55.000 --> 13:57.294
[Owen] <i>I'm vulnerable, but I'm not stupid.</i>

13:57.378 --> 14:01.006
[man] <i>But I will seek out the people</i>
<i>in my life that care about me.</i>

14:01.257 --> 14:04.260
[Owen] <i>I will seek out the people</i>
<i>in my life who care about me.</i>

14:04.343 --> 14:05.845
[man] <i>I am not the chosen one.</i>

14:06.178 --> 14:07.763
[Owen] <i>I am not the chosen one.</i>

14:07.847 --> 14:09.515
-[man] <i>The voices aren't real.</i>
-[clattering]

14:09.765 --> 14:11.892
-[Owen] <i>The voices aren't real.</i>
-The voices aren't real.

14:11.976 --> 14:13.644
[man] <i>The voices are just noise.</i>

14:13.727 --> 14:16.105
-[Owen] <i>The voices are just noise.</i>
