14:16.188 --> 14:19.316
[man] <i>I am just a guy</i>
<i>with a vivid imagination.</i>

14:19.733 --> 14:21.777
[Owen] <i>I'm just a guy</i>
<i>with a vivid imagination.</i>

14:21.861 --> 14:23.070
[doorbell rings]

14:23.153 --> 14:26.824
[man] <i>I will most likely</i>
<i>not be the savior of our galaxy.</i>

14:26.907 --> 14:27.825
Hello?

14:29.201 --> 14:32.913
[man, distorted] <i>I've got a package</i>
<i>from Neberdine Pharmaceutical Biotech</i>

14:32.997 --> 14:34.957
<i>for an Owen Milgrim.</i>

14:37.793 --> 14:38.669
What?

14:39.545 --> 14:41.547
[man] <i>I've... a package... your name.</i>

14:43.591 --> 14:44.884
[buzzing]

14:47.344 --> 14:49.179
[running footsteps]

14:49.263 --> 14:51.223
-[knock at door]
-[footsteps hurry away]

14:53.475 --> 14:54.852
[door slams downstairs]

15:02.026 --> 15:04.445
[telephone rings]

15:12.244 --> 15:13.078
Hello?

15:13.579 --> 15:15.873
[woman] <i>Hi, Owen.</i>
<i>Did you get what I sent you?</i>

15:16.206 --> 15:17.124
[Owen] How did you...

15:17.207 --> 15:20.628
[woman] <i>I've just been informed</i>
<i>that you qualify as a hero candidate.</i>

15:21.128 --> 15:23.005
-What does that mean?
<i>-</i>[woman] <i>It's a term we use</i>

15:23.088 --> 15:26.133
