Mustache. No, don't say anything.
Just be cool.

31:55.663 --> 31:57.040
The pattern is the pattern.

31:58.291 --> 31:59.542
The pattern got you here.

32:00.835 --> 32:02.170
Keep trusting the pattern.

32:03.087 --> 32:04.255
She's your handler now.

32:06.215 --> 32:08.259
She has a certain <i>je ne sais quoi.</i>

32:09.886 --> 32:11.137
She's no Olivia, though.

32:12.263 --> 32:14.599
Make contact with her.
Use the code phrase.

32:14.682 --> 32:19.312
[woman over PA] <i>If you are an odd number,</i>
<i>please line up at the intake corridor.</i>

32:19.395 --> 32:21.814
The pattern is the pattern.
I know it doesn't make sense.

32:21.898 --> 32:25.234
It doesn't make sense to me either
right now, but it will.

32:25.318 --> 32:27.737
Keep going forward.

32:27.820 --> 32:29.030
Just reach out...

32:30.239 --> 32:31.324
and make contact.

32:31.407 --> 32:35.161
[woman over PA] <i>All odd numbers,</i>
<i>line up by the intake corridor.</i>

32:47.674 --> 32:49.300
What the fuck is wrong with you?

32:49.717 --> 32:50.551
Sorry.

32:59.727 --> 33:00.937
[bleeping]

33:05.900 --> 33:07.360
[bleeping continues]

33:35.054 --> 33:36.097
Robert.

33:36.180 --> 33:38.391
[mumbling indistinctly]

33:38.474 --> 33:39.392
Robert. Robert, wake up.

33:42.061 --> 33:43.187
[grunts]

33:45.940 --> 33:47.191
The odds are here.

33:48.067 --> 33:48.901
Okay.

33:49.944 --> 33:53.031
Let us complete this trial
with none of the old problems, sir.

33:55.408 --> 33:56.868
Yes, Dr. Fujita.

33:57.410 --> 33:59.662
None of the old problems.

34:20.892 --> 34:22.435
[orderly] As you enter the common room,

34:22.518 --> 34:24.645
you will notice
there are numbers on the pods.

34:24.729 --> 34:27.982
The pod numbers correspond
with the numbers on your lanyards.

34:28.066 --> 34:29.442
Please go to your pod.

34:29.901 --> 34:33.154
That will be your home for the duration
of your stay here with us.

34:33.613 --> 34:35.865
Leaving your pod
at any unauthorized moment

34:35.948 --> 34:39.202
will result in the termination
of your stay here at this trial,

34:39.285 --> 34:42.497
as well as bringing shame
and humiliation upon you.

34:46.918 --> 34:49.545
Once you reach your pod,
an orderly will approach

34:49.629 --> 34:51.756
and begin to inspect your bag.

34:51.839 --> 34:55.551
Once the orderly has inspected your bag,
you will put your bag in your locker.

34:55.635 --> 34:57.887
Once you have done that,
make your way to this gentleman.

34:57.970 --> 34:59.305
He will give you your uniform,

34:59.388 --> 35:01.808
as well as your patented Neberdine shoes,

35:01.891 --> 35:05.061
which you cannot take with you
at the end of the trial.

35:07.480 --> 35:09.565
Once you have your uniforms
and your shoes,

35:09.649 --> 35:11.567
you will make your way back to your pods,

35:11.651 --> 35:15.530
then you will get in your pods
and change clothes in your pods.

35:15.613 --> 35:17.824
There will be no changing in the commons.

35:19.784 --> 35:21.285
Oh, my God!

35:21.369 --> 35:22.954
[orderly] Condoms are contraband.

35:23.037 --> 35:25.373
-Safety first.
-[orderly] That's a red flag right there.

35:25.456 --> 35:28.584
Intimacy in this facility is off-limits.

35:29.001 --> 35:32.630
There will be no cohabitation
inside the pods.

35:32.713 --> 35:35.258
Once the curfew starts, lights go out.

35:35.341 --> 35:36.926
You're not supposed to be here.

35:40.555 --> 35:41.389
Please.

35:41.472 --> 35:42.932
What are my instructions?

35:43.641 --> 35:44.976
The pattern is the pattern.

35:45.059 --> 35:47.228
You're my contact.
What are my instructions?

35:47.728 --> 35:50.481
[whispering] Please turn off the pattern.
Please turn off...

35:51.482 --> 35:53.025
-Owen.
-[orderly] ..tight schedule.

35:53.109 --> 35:54.944
We will tell you when there is mealtime.

35:55.027 --> 35:58.614
Your instructions are to go back
to your pod and await my signal.

35:58.698 --> 36:01.868
[orderly] ...two Etch A Sketches and one
Lite-Brite. Please don't fight over them.

36:01.951 --> 36:03.244
I'm going to save the world.

36:03.327 --> 36:05.288
We will tell you
when there's recreation time.

36:05.371 --> 36:06.914
-Yes.
-We will also tell you when...

36:06.998 --> 36:09.792
-You're gonna save the world.
-And we will tell you when to sleep.

36:09.876 --> 36:13.838
-But not if you blow our cover.
-[orderly] ...expecting. Thank you.

36:14.088 --> 36:15.548
Is that working for you?

36:15.631 --> 36:16.757
Okay, I understand.

36:16.841 --> 36:18.926
If you're having trouble
getting into your pod,

36:19.010 --> 36:23.472
there is also a little ladder underneath
that will help you get into your pod.

36:23.556 --> 36:25.641
Also note, from here on in,

36:25.725 --> 36:28.978
you will be referred to
as the number on your lanyard.

36:29.061 --> 36:30.104
You are the Odds.

36:32.231 --> 36:33.065
Attention.

36:44.076 --> 36:48.080
Please give your attention
to Dr. Muramoto and Dr. Fujita.

36:48.164 --> 36:50.082
They will be supervising your trials.

36:50.750 --> 36:51.959
[speaking in Japanese]

36:53.836 --> 36:55.213
Welcome, subjects.

36:55.713 --> 36:57.757
You made the right choice.

36:58.299 --> 37:01.844
It's time to start your lives again.

37:05.139 --> 37:06.766
You don't fuck this up...

37:08.017 --> 37:09.602
I won't fuck this up.

37:10.645 --> 37:11.604
Just kidding.

37:24.158 --> 37:25.409
[sighs]
